divs: sighting detailsfirst event was at approx 7:45pm fri jan 28th,i went onto the deck & looking up at the stars a bright star like object shot up & disappeared after about 3-4 seconds.i got on sky view cafe to see what the stars were around where i saw this-it's close to adara. after looking at this i went back out on the deck apporx 10 mins later & saw a boomerang shape with 2 side & a center orangish\reddish glow -not really bright at all,it looked like it was foggy around the obrs-couldn't see any type of "frame" but it was a perfect boomerang shape.it was 300-500 ft off the ground & i watched it from over 127th st.until it went out of my sight over 119th st.probably 6-10 secs or so.i yelled for my daughter to come out & by the time she got there it was out of sight-the width-if you held your arms out at shoulder width up to the sky would be the apporx width between the outside 2 orbs-huge.there was no sound at all-my dog was outside but didn't react.it basically went right over my neighbors house from south to north.this was totally amazing-they're real,they're here,just not sure why.
